snippet.title: Legerdemain - A Tale Fraught with Peril and Wonder
snippet.description: Surreal and vast, Legerdemain is a roguelike RPG set in the strange world of Phenomedom. Sit back and have a cup of zing as we observe the first three weeks in the adventures of one Mr. Swift, a manipulator of Chronos who, in the years that followed, would go on to greatness.
